  <brief_title>A Study Evaluating Lanreotide as Maintenance Therapy in Patients With Non-Resectable Duodeno-Pancreatic Neuroendocrine Tumors (REMINET)</brief_title>
  <acronym>REMINET</acronym>
  <official_title>A EUROPEAN, MULTICENTRE, PHASE II/III RANDOMISED DOUBLE-BLIND, PLACEBO CONTROLLED STUDY EVALUATING LANREOTIDE AS MAINTENANCE THERAPY IN PATIENTS WITH NON-RESECTABLE DUODENO-PANCREATIC NEUROENDOCRINE TUMOURS AFTER FIRST-LINE TREATMENT</official_title>
